{"id":87693,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/07/upcoming-gmail-features/","date":"2010-07-31T12:50:43Z","modified":"2010-07-31T12:50:43Z","title":"Upcoming Gmail Features","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/3740/2\">Google Operating System &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年07月30日,  已有 9 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>How many changes can you spot in this screenshot of an internal version of Gmail from the Chromium OS bug tracker?</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_ZaGO7GjCqAI/TFMC5wYaPdI/AAAAAAAAW5c/VmkZoMrlaVc/s640/gmail-googler-ui-2010-2.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br /><img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_ZaGO7GjCqAI/TFMC6Ee1bvI/AAAAAAAAW5k/Q4HSClIbd6s/s640/gmail-googler-ui-2010.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />Here&#8217;s what I noticed: there are three links for &#8220;mail&#8221;, &#8220;contacts&#8221; and &#8220;tasks&#8221; below Gmail&#8217;s logo, there&#8217;s a new button for composing messages, a &#8220;<a href=\"http://googlesystem.blogspot.com/2010/06/google-voice-to-integrate-with-gmail-as.html\">call phone</a>&#8221; option in Gmail Chat, a drop-down for <a href=\"http://googlesystem.blogspot.com/2010/07/google-tests-multiple-accounts-sign-in.html\">switching between Google accounts</a> and the options that let you select unread or starred messages use less space.</p>\n<p>{ Thanks, Mateo. }</p>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/18157064-1168503690005473942?l=googlesystem.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/GoogleOperatingSystem?a=WdpE-Cf_li4:WXIYfZEzTd4:4cEx4HpKnUU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/GoogleOperatingSystem?i=WdpE-Cf_li4:WXIYfZEzTd4:4cEx4HpKnUU\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/GoogleOperatingSystem?a=WdpE-Cf_li4:WXIYfZEzTd4:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/GoogleOperatingSystem?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/GoogleOperatingSystem?a=WdpE-Cf_li4:WXIYfZEzTd4:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/GoogleOperatingSystem?i=WdpE-Cf_li4:WXIYfZEzTd4:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/GoogleOperatingSystem?a=WdpE-Cf_li4:WXIYfZEzTd4:-BTjWOF_DHI\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/GoogleOperatingSystem?i=WdpE-Cf_li4:WXIYfZEzTd4:-BTjWOF_DHI\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/GoogleOperatingSystem?a=WdpE-Cf_li4:WXIYfZEzTd4:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/GoogleOperatingSystem?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/GoogleOperatingSystem/~4/WdpE-Cf_li4\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/1017243/tongji.gif\" /><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/997968/tongji.gif\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://googlesystem.blogspot.com/2010/07/upcoming-gmail-features.html\" title=\"Upcoming Gmail Features\">Upcoming Gmail Features</a></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[5908]}